      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_60ADD280-E0DB-0138-3FA4-12F2183ABDFB" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If you want to mark a conversation as unread, click the read indicator [1]. The message will now show the unread indicator [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
