  <div id="text-content_60AE0C30-E0DB-0138-3FA7-12F2183ABDFB" class="text-block-content">
    <p>You can mark multiple conversations as unread or read by pressing the command key (Mac) or the control key (Windows) while clicking multiple messages, or by selecting the message checkbox [1].</p>
<p>Locate and click the settings icon and choose the <strong>Mark all as unreadÂ </strong>link [2].</p>
<p>If you select multiple unread messages, you will see <strong>Mark all as read</strong> link [3].</p>
